      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a dependable commuter or family car. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal wear and tear, such as small surface scratches or light stone chips, the paint still retains a nice luster. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as intended. It has a consistent maintenance history and is ready for its next owner to enjoy many more miles of reliable service.",
